CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Anghami Inc is a digital music entertainment technology platform in the Middle East and North Africa, with the largest catalog of songs. The company features licensed content from leading Arabic labels, independent artists, and distributors. It also features music from the major International labels such as Universal, Sony, Warner and is continuously licensing new content.
